n is a monotonically\nincreasing function of time for any $q_0$, suggesting that the binary growth by\naccretion does not lead to the formation of close binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2016 08:33:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2016 10:29:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-14"}
