ly, \"From gas\nand dust to stars and planets\".\n  FLARE will provide to the ESA community a leading position to statistically\nstudy the early universe after JWST's deep but pin-hole surveys. Moreover, the\ninstrumental development of wide-field imaging and wide-field integral-field\nspectroscopy in space will be a major breakthrough after making them available\non ground-based telescopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2016 09:18:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-12"}
