om the rotation period, we find that the hot side of\nthe LDB is fitted well by Li EW values corresponding to an age of 25$\\pm$3 Myr\nin good agreement with independent estimates from the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2016 11:20:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2016 08:23:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-30"}
