xt part of the White Paper we outline other interesting options for SDMM that\ncould be studied in more detail in the future. Finally, we discuss important\naspects of supersymmetric models for DM and how these could help to develop of\nmore complete SDMM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2016 13:45:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2016 08:33:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 25 Feb 2017 12:16:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-28"}
